	   <tr><td colspan=2>As an SK at lvl 15 you will be able to scribe mem and cast &quot;Endure Cold&quot; the effect of which is to provide +10 SvCld.&nbsp;&nbsp;This spell seems essentially uswless to an SK but be assured it is not.  Cast this spell every chance you get from 15 through to lvl 30.  The reason being it is the only abjuration spell you have until you get Feign Death not just useful but one of the class defining abilities/spells of an SK, and endure cold is the only way to get your abjuration up to scratch so that you can actually rely on FD to work for you when you get it.  If you do not practice your endure cold you may find yourself chaincasting Endure cold sveral hundred times to improve your Abjuration at lvl 30.<br>&nbsp;<br>Good, evil, I'm just a Troll with a Noctavigent Blade<br><br>Hatre Danpayne<br>40th Lvl Troll Shadowknight<br>&lt;Ebon Tendrils&gt;<br>Xegony Server</td></tr>
