	   <tr><td colspan=2>You will probably get a ton of varying thoughts on this.&nbsp;&nbsp;I can only give you my thoughts, which Im certain many will tell me that I am high or something....  =P<br><br>My thoughts are, since you said already you wanted an SK, make it a Gnome and have fun.  Put all your bonus points into Stamina.  <br><br>Since you do not have a main character to feed you pp, you will have a little bit of a challenge starting from scratch, but, especially with the bazaar, you can get decent items for uber cheap.  <br><br>Therefore, I would just focus on leveling.  The harder mobs you kill, in general, the more $$ they will drop.  Accumulate a little bit at a time and begin your spending spree.<br><br>If you are lucky enough to make friends with a high level SK, you might be able to get some gifts, as some (like me) have banks overflowing with crap....  -)<br><br>Luna<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
