	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well,<br><br>Maybe a little..<br>when being powerlvled you prolly won't tank the mobs wich causing your defensive skills not to raise.<br>When equipping a very good weapon, or get xp from not really attacking the mobs that much, your weapons skill won't grow that much.<br><br>Wich causes your ATK and AC and dogde,riposte, etc to be lower at the higher lvl you became.<br><br>At that time your have a little tougher time getting xp at all, but when you can get in a group at that time, your build that skill up rather quickly, so all in all your character based skills won't suffer much.<br><br>I do however agree with the other person, that you can miss learning playing skills.<br>&nbsp;<br>With kind regards,<br><br>Khawain Ogre Shadowknight - Tallon Zek<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=311293" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=311293</a></td></tr>
