	   <tr><td colspan=2>Mess up your character badly?&nbsp;&nbsp;Not sure I agree with that.  Mess up your skills as a player?  Perhaps....<br><br>I think what the person is referring to, when powerleveling, is that you might not learn certain skills that you otherwise would learn when you are getting power leveled.<br><br>I can assure you that, at times, there is little to no risk from getting powerleveled.  I know from personal expereicne that some levels were nothing more than a time sink and if I was somehow able to speed that process up, there would have been substantially nothing but benefit.<br><br>However, if you somehow got power leveled right into your mid 50s, say, and you really didnt learn that much along the way, then yeah, there would probably be some negative ramifications of that.<br><br>As far as what skills you need to be on the look out for....heh....not sure I have enough room.<br><br>=)<br><br>Luna<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
